## To set up dbt (Data Build Tool) on macOS, you can follow these steps:
## https://docs.getdbt.com/docs/core/installation-overview
## https://docs.getdbt.com/docs/core/pip-install
## https://softwarevipra.medium.com/dbt-data-build-tool-setup-on-mac-c3dbe3e6872f


Step:1 Create a new venv:
    - python -m venv dbt-env # create the environment

Step:2 Activate that same virtual environment each time you create a shell window or session:
    - source dbt-env/bin/activate # activate the environment for Mac and Linux OR

Step:3 Installing adapter:
    - python -m pip install \
      dbt-core \
      dbt-postgres

Step:4 Test the installed dbt:
    - dbt --version

Step:5 Init dbt project:
    - dbt init my_postgres_db

Step:6 Follow the instruction to configure connection:

Step:7 Test the connection:
    - dbt debug
